    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "H8VbzqWWhrj4"
      },
      "source": [
        "There is a problem that these reviews contain html tags,special characters that do not help us in analysis , so we need to clean the data"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "j6winNLTiFxs"
      },
      "source": [
        "# Text Cleaning\n",
        "1.Sample 10000  rows(taking 10000 values for training and testing the model)\n",
        "       \n",
        "2.Remove Html Tags\n",
        "\n",
        "3.Remove special characters\n",
        "\n",
        "4.Converting every thing into lowercase\n",
        "\n",
        "5.Removing stop words(words like and,if,the...they do not help to build sentiment)\n",
        "\n",
        "6.Stemming (some words are present in different words like play,playing,played we will stem down them to their basic form play)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "QRNAjeyOheds"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "df = df.sample(\n",
        "    22000,\n",
        "    random_state=42\n",
        ")"
      ]
    },
